# Caddyfile — stockmanagement.app  (subdomain-per-client hosting)
#
# Caddy automatically obtains + renews HTTPS certificates for the main domain
# and every client subdomain listed here. Add one block per client (the
# `provision-client` script prints the exact block), then run:  caddy reload
#
# DNS: a wildcard  *.stockmanagement.app  A-record must point at this server,
# plus  stockmanagement.app  itself, so every subdomain resolves here.
#
# NOTE: .app is HTTPS-only (HSTS preload). Caddy's auto-HTTPS covers this — there
# is nothing extra to configure; plain http:// simply isn't offered.

# --- Main domain: landing page / demo instance ---
stockmanagement.app, www.stockmanagement.app {
    reverse_proxy localhost:4000
}

# --- One block per client (each = its own instance + database) ---
# provision-client prints the exact block. Example:
# beta.stockmanagement.app {
#     reverse_proxy localhost:4001
# }

# acme.stockmanagement.app {
#     reverse_proxy localhost:4002
# }
